acf-stepca © Corey De Lasaux 2024 <cordelster@gmail.com>


## Dependancies
- step-certificates 
- step-badger (https://github.com/lukasz-lobocki/step-badger) -installed in either /usr/bin, /usr/local/bin
  step-badger is used where step-ca cli falls short to view catalog and cert status more specificly around 
  revoked certs. It's optional, and just provides better information, and speeds up some of the queries..
- jq

## Description

Initialize and manage Step certificates from Alpine Linux ACF. 

